    "question_id" : 224311,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>The class <code>BooleanUtils</code> supportes the negation of a boolean. You find this class in <a href=\"https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.apache.commons/commons-lang3\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">commons-lang:commons-lang</a> </p>\n\n<pre><code>BooleanUtils.negate(theBoolean)\n</code></pre>\n"
