    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can use ternary operator to have a clean conditional statement</p>\n<pre><code>theBoolean = theBoolean?false:true;\n</code></pre>\n<p>I believe this to be the most efficient toggle statement without the use of any fancy functions.</p>\n"
