  "title" : "Cleanest way to toggle a boolean variable in Java?",
  "body" : "<p>Is there a better way to negate a boolean in Java than a simple if-else?</p>\n\n<pre><code>if (theBoolean) {\n    theBoolean = false;\n} else {\n    theBoolean = true;\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
